      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the info. since i'm really desperate to sleep, i was thinking maybe i could up the melatonin to like 10mg or so tonight with the ambien? i feel like if i take a bigger dose of the melatonin it'll just kick in stronger with the prescription. if i do that it shouldn't be a big deal right? it's just a natural supplement anyway.",
